text: Jackie Gowler (born 7 June 1996) is a New Zealand representative rower. She won a gold medal as a member of the women's eight team at the 2019 World Rowing Championships, alongside her elder sister Kerri Gowler. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1996 births Category:New Zealand female rowers Category:World Rowing Championships medalists for New Zealand Category:Rowers at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics
